30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T16:11:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DThpcMfL3dI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDThpcMfL3dI&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=9a86e164\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DThpcMfL3dI</a><br />\n<br />\n三十年前今日，條片有幾多偽人？ <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab293c353fd236268ba45d19acebcf8a9bc84ee8","tid":1180814,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:10:14.000Z","msg":"腳趾姐！！何婉盈出新歌！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就出慘情合唱歌　何婉盈預告一年內開騷<br />\n<br />\n歌手何婉盈、胡渭康、黎明詩及陸家俊晚上到尖沙咀出席電影首映，何婉盈透露最近頻頻有歌唱工作，七月會擔任演唱會嘉賓，之後亦會做群星騷，問到會否開個人騷？她說：「我有咁意思，籌備中，但唔想開空頭支票，希望係一年內。（出新歌？）一定要有！最近李健達邀請我合唱，有廣東話同國語版。（有冇信心好似當年同曾航生首《再見亦是朋友》咁Hit？）呢首都係差不多，我幾首歌都係傷感，今次都係慘情歌。（有冇開始練歌練氣？）上星期開始上堂跳舞同健身，真係要Keep吓，希望上台可以瘦啲。」她大讚好友胡渭康及曾航生保養得宜，胡渭康更猶如吃了防腐劑一樣，自己都要努力Keep Fit。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190606/bkn-20190606075240799-0606_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190606%2Fbkn-20190606075240799-0606_00862_001.html&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=ac6a05f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190606/bkn-20190606075240799-0606_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0403c3b253c18442e4a4d6e573d0bff14c195563","tid":1180814,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:32:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"ht